In order to run this application:
1. please compile all .sql scripts inside the sql folder of the project
2. modify the server.js file at line 13 and 14 and enter your db credentials within double quotes. line 13 for username and line 14 for password.
3. Open the terminal inside the project folder and execute the following command: node server.js
4. if the previous command did not work, please download and install node.js on your local machine by following these steps https://docs.npmjs.com/downloading-and-installing-node-js-and-npm
5. The application should be started by now and will be accessible at http://localhost:3000
